title: Duke Energy Renewables achieves momentous safety milestone (Duke Energy Corporation)
text: ( Source : Duke Energy Corporation ) CHARLOTTE , N.C. - Duke Energy Renewables and its third-party services group, Duke Energy Renewable Services, have completed one year and counting without an Occupational Safety and Health Administration
